Package com.github.yeetmanlord.zeta_core.logging

Class ConsoleLogger

java.lang.Object
com.github.yeetmanlord.zeta_core.logging.ConsoleLogger
public class ConsoleLogger extends Object
Custom ZetaPlugin logger. It supports colors and formatting unlike Log4J logger. Technically a wrapper for Bukkit's logger. But I want it to sound cool.
Author:
YeetManLord
Plugin Usage:
